CS3410 Video Game Design and Development
Fall 2018

Teapots Unity Game Project
-Full Unity Project packaged in "Teapots.7z"
-Copies of my C# scripts are in "ScriptCopies" folder

Game Description:
-Game is played using arrow keys and space bar
-There are multiple floating teapots that player must knock down with cannonballs
-Arrow keys: moves position of the camera
-Space bar: shoots out a cannonball
-Timer of 30 seconds counts down on start up
-"Game Over" is displayed after 30 seconds and teapots still remain unknocked
-"You Win" is displayed after knocking down all teapots within 30 seconds
